---
title: Sweet Pepper and Black Bean Pork Chorizo Taquitos with Monterey Jack Cheese and Fresh Salad
description: Nutritious and delicious black beans take centre stage in this fun recipe. Cooked with sweet onions, peppers and zesty chipotle sauce, everything is then wrapped and baked with stretchy Monterey Jack cheese for ultimate cheese pull satisfaction!
